import React from 'react'
import {Container ,Content ,Title ,Desc  ,Line ,Lines ,Row  ,Card} from './style'
const Project = () => {
    return (
      <Container>
          <Content>
            <Title>Our project </Title>
            <Desc>Introducing our first official project</Desc>
             <Line>
               <Lines></Lines>
               <Lines></Lines>
             </Line>
          </Content>

          <Row>
               <Card>
                      <CardHeader>
                               
                      </CardHeader>
               </Card>
          </Row>
      </Container>
    )
}

export default Project
